snippet.title: Texas Educators Use Canvas for Blended and Personalized Learning
snippet.description: We are continually amazed at the incredible work our customers are doing. During this session, we want to highlight a group of educators from Austin ISD. This group of Expert Educators from Texas have  developed two signature programs using Canvas to deliver blended and personalized learning to educators on transformative technology and problem-based learning. Join this session to learn how they did it, and what they are doing to keep the learning process thriving during the pandemic
